# Code Comments Standards

- **Minimal commenting** - Only add comments for hard parts or complex logic
- **Concise and clear** - When comments are needed, they must be brief and explain the "why" not the "what"
- **Self-documenting code** - Prefer clear variable names and structure over comments
- Avoid obvious comments that just restate what the code does
